topIssues.title: [Marketing] Brand Strategy & Launch Preparation
topIssues.author: borisudovicic
topIssues.body:
## Description

Brand strategy and marketing preparation for Eliza App launch, including influencer outreach, core messaging, and character file review.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Identify top influential friends in the space for private access
- [ ] Create "leak" concept for early access campaign
- [ ] Compile list of interesting use cases by niche
- [ ] Core messaging document from PRD (needs team review)
- [ ] Review and refine Eliza character file
- [ ] Share materials in Eliza App channel for feedback

## Technical Notes

**From Jan 28, 2026 meeting (Amelia):**

* "Ben and I connected this morning. He's tackling some of the initial seeding for the campaign."
* "Identifying essentially our top influential friends in the space and giving them private access first"
* "Creating this concept of a leak"
* "Getting into some of the more fun ways that you can use Eliza"
* "Created a list of interesting ideas based off of different niches"
* "Made a core messaging document mainly from Boris's PRD"
* "Going through the Eliza character now"

## Deliverables

* Influencer/friends list for early access
* Niche use case ideas document
* Core messaging document (from PRD)
* Eliza character file review notes

## Priority

**P1 - Marketing prep for launch**

topIssues.title: [Agent] Auto Agent VPS Security Sandbox & Twitter Integration
topIssues.author: borisudovicic
topIssues.body:
## Description

Set up security sandbox for auto agent VPS and get Twitter integration working properly.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [X] Security sandbox created for auto VPS (no credentials exposed)
- [X] Agent can make tweets
- [ ] Agent can read mentions
- [ ] Full Twitter integration working

## Technical Notes

**From Jan 28, 2026 meeting (R Odili):**

* "I made a little security sandbox so the auto VPS has no credentials"
* "Got that worked out yesterday"
* "He's able to make a tweet but he's not able to read mention"
* "Going to continue debugging and working on that today"

## Current Status

* Security sandbox complete
* Tweet posting works
* Mention reading not working - debugging in progress

## Priority

**P1 - In Progress**
